Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,FORGE. Forecasted Onset of Rotational-Gear Endpoint. Predictive\Nbearing-failure for the Marine ground fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,MARADMIN 131/26 calls for AI to anticipate equipment failure and\Nimprove readiness. We answer it for MTVR, JLTV, and LAV-25 wheel hubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick MTVR-2491. 12 kHz drive-end accelerometer, 1-second window —\Nspectrogram and envelope spectrum render with BPFO, BPFI, BSF …
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Classifier flags OUTER RACE FAULT with high confidence. Remaining\Nuseful life: about 118 operating hours. Rule-based call: INDUCT NOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.10,0:00:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Multimodal LLM agent reads the spectrogram image, the classifier\Noutput, the 6-month maintenance log, and a parts-availability tool …
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.12,0:00:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It outputs a structured JSON recommendation: induct now, NSN 3110 in\Nstock — 14 on the shelf at Albany.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:01:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Powered by a Kamiwaza-deployed model. Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL to\Nkamiwaza.local for fully on-prem inference. Same code. Air-gapped. …
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,FORGE. Built on the Kamiwaza Stack. Deploy in hours, not months.
